tlight_attempts (id INTEGER PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, created_at TEXT NOT NULL, sentence TEXT NOT NULL, stressed_indices TEXT NOT NULL, user_indices TEXT NOT NULL, precision REAL NOT NULL, recall REAL NOT NULL, shadow_score REAL)\" (CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS is acceptable here because the table is brand new — no ALTER needed). This is distinct from #666 Thought-Group Phrasing (which is about pause/chunk boundaries) and from any shadowing card because the core skill is identifying which individual words carry prominence.",
